name: Seems like I'm a third wheel in that scenario.
description: The third picture of the three. Mini-collection «love, Sex, Universe».  I imagined that our Universe was a vast ocean filled with lustful and dangerous mermaids, scheming jellyfish, and lovesick seahorses. This artwork is in a single copy. All the original materials have been destroyed.  Parameters: 1024x512 pixels, 300 dpi.
